em); and the other is a very complex and also a symbiotic\nfission-fusion-fission system composed by layers of the thermonuclear fuels\nLiDT, LiD and a highly-supercritical fission fuel. The last is considered an\nextreme case for testing the time-dependent neutron transport solution\npresented here.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2017 14:04:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2017 15:25:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2017 18:04:07 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2017 21:03:46 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2017 19:48:05 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Mon, 22 May 2017 16:41:04 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Tue, 23 May 2017 18:49:30 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Tue, 6 Feb 2018 20:43:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-08"}
